flowchart LR
    Client[Voice Client or Telephony Adapter]
    WS[Fastify WebSocket /ws]
    STT[Deepgram Live STT]
    LLM[Groq-hosted LLM]
    TTS[Cartesia Streaming TTS]
    Redis[(Redis TTL Memory)]
    Postgres[(Postgres)]
    Tools[Appointment Tools]
    Campaigns[Outbound Campaign Session Bootstrap]

    Client -->|audio chunks| WS
    WS --> STT
    STT -->|final transcript| LLM
    LLM -->|token stream| WS
    WS --> TTS
    TTS -->|audio stream| Client

    LLM <--> Redis
    LLM <--> Postgres
    LLM --> Tools
    Tools <--> Postgres
    Campaigns --> Redis
    Campaigns --> Postgres
    Campaigns --> WS
